quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  7,118,"Basi chasimichiche chakuona ni yaweseche yaŵaliji nkutenda."
  7,119,"Basi niŵapundidwe palakwepo niŵasyuchile kuŵa ŵakunyosyeka."
  7,120,"Asaŵi ni ŵaligwisyisye pasi kusujudu."
  8,52,"(Nyendele ja makafili galeloga jili) chisawu nyendele ja ŵandu ŵa Firiauna ni aŵala ŵapaujo pao, ŵakanile imanyilo ya Allah, basi Allah ni ŵakwembekenye ligongo lya sambi syao, chisimu Allah ni Jwakulimbangana nnope, Jwaukali kusyene pakupeleka ipotesi."
  8,53,"Yalakweyi niligongo lyanti Allah nganaŵa jwanti ni kuchigalausya chindimba chaŵapele ŵandu mpaka ali agalawisye (ŵanduo) umbone wauli m’mitima mwao, soni chisimu Allah ni Jwakupikanichisya, Jwakumanyilila nnope."
  8,54,"(Nyendele ja makafili galeloga jili) chisawu nyendele ja ŵandu ŵa Firiauna ni aŵala ŵapaujo pao, ŵakaaniile imanyilo ya M’mbuje gwao (Allah), basi ni twaajonasile ligongo lya sambi syao, ni twamisyisye ŵandu ŵa Firiauna, soni wosope ŵaliji ŵakulitenda lupuso."
  9,22,"Chakaŵe ŵandamo mwalakwemo kwa yaka ni yaka. Chisimu Allah Kukwakwe kwana malipilo gamakulungwa nnope."
  9,23,"E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Ngasimwatenda achatati ŵenu ni achachimwene ŵenu kuŵa isyoŵe naga ali awunonyele ukafili m’malo mwa chikulupi. Sano jwachiŵatende kuŵa isyoŵe yakwe mwa jenumanja, basi ŵanganyao ni ŵali ŵakulitenda lupuso."
  9,24,"Jilani: “Naŵaga achatati ŵenu, ŵanache ŵenu, achachimwene ŵenu, achiŵammakwenu, achanasi ŵenu, kwisa soni ipanje yanyyipatile, ni malonda gankugajogopela konasika, kwisa soni majumba gankuganonyela, (naiŵaga yalakweyi) yakunonyeledwa nnope kukwenu kumpunda Allah ni Ntenga Jwakwe ﷺ ni kumenyana ngondo petala Lyakwe; basi jembecheyani kwikanila Allah ayiche ni chilamusi Chakwe (cha ipotesi), soni Allah ngaakwajongolaga ŵandu ŵakunyosya.”"